Lakehouse architecture is revolutionizing the field of data management! By merging the strengths of data lakes and data warehouses into a cohesive system, it provides a comprehensive solution for storing, managing, and analyzing data at scale. This approach is designed to tackle the limitations and challenges associated with traditional data warehouses and data lakes. 

If you're interested in exploring this emerging approach, check out the lakehouse reference architectures available. 

https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/databricks/lakehouse-architecture/reference
